            "processed": "<p>Quote:</p><blockquote><p><span>The Pairwise Stitching first queries for two input images that you intend to stitch. They can contain rectangular ROIs which limit the search to those areas, however, the full images will be stitched together. Once you selected the input images it will show the actual dialog for the Pairwise Stitching.</span></p></blockquote>",
